title: 11/12 Fantasy Football Podcast: Week 10 Recap - Expect the Unexpected
description:
We review the big RB injuries to start the show and then get into our winners (5:45) like Jared Goff and Davante Adams (12:56) and losers (19:50) including Marvin Jones and Melvin Gordon (21:54) ... Week 10 was unpredictable! We react to big games from Kirk Cousins and Case Keenum (24:51), Leonard Fournette's dud (28:15), Ameer Abdullah finding the end zone (29:05), DAL without Zeke and Tyron Smith (34:00) and much more ... Leaders at each position (37:02), a discussion about TE depth and a recap of every game with our Fantasy takes (43:30) ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
